Package: xlsform2wordRev
Type: Package
Title: Convert XLSForm to Word , FR Language-Aware Choices and Conditions
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person( "Manantsoa",  "Vagnondily", role = c("aut","cre"),
           email = "vagnondily@proton.me")
Description: Read an XLSForm and produce a formatted Word (.docx) questionnaire. 
    Highlights relevant conditions in red,
    and substitutes choice names by localized labels based on survey label language.
